      {
        "id": "commentary-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 38,
          "end": 40
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "漢武紀曰始元二年閏九月遣故廷尉王平等五人持節行郡國舉賢良問民所疾苦寃失職者顔師古曰前為此官今不居者皆謂之故也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 40,
          "end": 69
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "修務訓曰所為言者齊於衆而同於俗今不稱九天之頂則言黃泉之底是兩末之端議何可以公論乎",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-18",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "音扶",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-19",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 37
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "原道訓曰禹之決瀆也因水以為師神農之播榖也因苗以為教",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-20",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 37,
          "end": 38
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
